  "body": "### Description\n\nSee https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/issues/20959 - the user is reporting that AWS ALB is not appropriately including \\:authority nor x-forwarded- for http/2 requests.  The resulting behavior for keycloak is to resolve 0.0.0.0 as the host.\r\n\r\nIt would appear this behavior by the ALB is not compliant with https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc9113.html#section-8.3.1-1 so this is being captured as an enhancement, rather than a bug.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
